Toleni&#8217;s suspected murderer, a 30-year-old shepherd, was yesterday charged with a slew of serious crimes, among themkilling matriculant Nandipha Mtuzula, 19, in the appearance at Butterworth Magistrate s Court. In a startling revelation, police said three more teenage girls from one school in the area had also gone missing and turned up dead.Police yesterday said they were trying to establish whether or not the cases were linked. The man, who cannot be named as he was not asked to plead, is now facing additional chargesTo read more, get a copy of the Daily Dispatch, or subscribe to our e-edition.